    <title>搭建图床</title>
    <link href="https://1232333.xyz/2020/04/03/%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E5%9B%BE%E5%BA%8A/"/>
    <id>https://1232333.xyz/2020/04/03/搭建图床/</id>
    <published>2020-04-03T11:10:10.000Z</published>
    <updated>2020-04-04T13:19:05.562Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="PicGo-Gitee-Github-个人图床"><a href="#PicGo-Gitee-Github-个人图床" class="headerlink" title="PicGo+Gitee+Github|个人图床"></a>PicGo+Gitee+Github|个人图床</h1><h2 id="一，注册-软件准备"><a href="#一，注册-软件准备" class="headerlink" title="一，注册+软件准备"></a>一，注册+软件准备</h2><p>​        我们先到github<a href="https://github.com/join?source=header-home" target="_blank" rel="noopener">官网注册</a>+gitee<a href="https://gitee.com/signup" target="_blank" rel="noopener">官网</a>一个用户名+下载<a href="https://github.com/Molunerfinn/PicGo/releases" target="_blank" rel="noopener">PicGo</a>,下载PicGo要科学上网如果你没有也可以在我的<a href="https://www.lanzous.com/b0f1fslqh" target="_blank" rel="noopener">蓝奏云</a>里下载。关于注册github和gitee我在这里就不赘述了。国外推荐用github国内推荐用gitee,我觉得这取决于用户的体验感，github在国内不用cdn加速，hhh，还是用吧，jsDelivr。网上教程也是多的一批主要还是给我的几位小童鞋咳咳。</p><h2 id="二，Gitee上的仓库"><a href="#二，Gitee上的仓库" class="headerlink" title="二，Gitee上的仓库"></a>二，Gitee上的仓库</h2><p>​          gitee右上角新建一个仓库</p><p><img src="https://gitee.com/ojbkxc/PicGo/raw/master/img/20200403182346.png" alt></p><p>依次填入仓库名称和路径，一定要公开把这个勾选上</p><p>这里加一个选项，使用Readme文件初始化这个仓库</p><p><img src="https://gitee.com/ojbkxc/PicGo/raw/master/img/20200403181901.png" alt></p><p>在-设置-私有令牌-生成新令牌（右上角）</p><p><img src="https://gitee.com/ojbkxc/PicGo/raw/master/img/20200403181735.png" alt></p><p><img src="https://gitee.com/ojbkxc/PicGo/raw/master/img/20200403181349.png" alt></p><p> 我们把图中的权限选上再提交</p><p><img src="https://gitee.com/ojbkxc/PicGo/raw/master/img/20200403181609.png" alt></p><p>再输入gitee的密码进行验证</p><p><img src="https://gitee.com/ojbkxc/PicGo/raw/master/img/20200403182527.png" alt></p><p>之后会弹出私人令牌，自己拷贝保存一下以后用着也方便</p><p><img src="https://gitee.com/ojbkxc/PicGo/raw/master/img/20200403182446.png" alt></p><h2 id="三，Github上的仓库"><a href="#三，Github上的仓库" class="headerlink" title="三，Github上的仓库"></a>三，Github上的仓库</h2><p>获取Github我们先到官网跟gitee一样的去新建仓库，一定要公开</p><p><img src="https://gitee.com/ojbkxc/PicGo/raw/master/img/20200403183648.png" alt></p><p><img src="https://gitee.com/ojbkxc/PicGo/raw/master/img/20200403184129.png" alt></p><p>然后一样的去获取Token码</p><p><img src="https://gitee.com/ojbkxc/PicGo/raw/master/img/20200403184306.png" alt></p><p><img src="https://gitee.com/ojbkxc/PicGo/raw/master/img/20200403184352.png" alt></p><p>个人访问令牌</p><p><img src="https://gitee.com/ojbkxc/PicGo/raw/master/img/20200403184649.png" alt></p><p>生成新令牌</p><p><img src="https://gitee.com/ojbkxc/PicGo/raw/master/img/20200403184719.png" alt></p><p>然后输入github密码验证</p><p><img src="https://gitee.com/ojbkxc/PicGo/raw/master/img/20200403184533.png" alt></p><p>我们把Select scopes下的这几个选上</p><p>下面的加选项口</p><p> repo        Full control of private repositories</p><ul><li>repo:status                            Access commit status<ul><li>repo_deployment                Access deployment status<ul><li>public_repo                Access public repositories</li><li>repo:invite            Access repository invitations</li></ul></li></ul></li></ul><p><img src="https://gitee.com/ojbkxc/PicGo/raw/master/img/20200403184820.png" alt></p><p><img src="https://gitee.com/ojbkxc/PicGo/raw/master/img/20200403185439.png" alt></p><p>自己拷贝保存一下以后用得到</p><p><img src="https://gitee.com/ojbkxc/PicGo/raw/master/img/20200403185552.png" alt></p><p>下面是GitHub的配置</p><p>设定仓库名：    用户名/仓库名</p><p>设定分支名：    master</p><p>设定Token:        将上面获得的Token填上去</p><p>指定存储路径：    img/</p><p>设定自定义域名：    <a href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/用户名/仓库名" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/用户名/仓库名</a>            （jsDelivr提速）</p><p><img src="https://gitee.com/ojbkxc/PicGo/raw/master/img/20200403185645.png" alt><br>我们打开安装好的PicGo里面的插件设置，搜索gitee的插件，安装右侧的gitee-uploader 1.1.2<img src="https://gitee.com/ojbkxc/PicGo/raw/master/img/20200403182826.png" alt></p><p>接着我们输入</p><p>repo:        用户名/仓库名</p><p>branch:        master</p><p>token:        这里填你刚才获得的私人令牌</p><p>path:        img/</p><p>最后一个不填</p><p><img src="https://gitee.com/ojbkxc/PicGo/raw/master/img/20200403183054.png" alt></p><h2 id="四，演示"><a href="#四，演示" class="headerlink" title="四，演示"></a>四，演示</h2><p>我们去设置里面把-时间戳重命名_打开</p><p><img src="https://gitee.com/ojbkxc/PicGo/raw/master/img/20200403190356.png" alt></p><p>我们任意选择一个图床，以及下面需要生成的链接格式，我此时写作的是Typora所以……Markdown,链接格式情节于你的需求，当然如果你从未用过Typora的话也可以在兴趣的范围去<a href="https://typora.io/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">官网</a>下载以此记录笔记。</p><p><img src="https://gitee.com/ojbkxc/PicGo/raw/master/img/20200403190606.png" alt></p><p>然后将任意一张图片拖动到上传区_上传</p><p><img src="https://gitee.com/ojbkxc/PicGo/raw/master/img/20200403190757.png" alt></p><p>上传成功之后在右下角会有上传成功的提示，之后会自动复制在你的粘贴板中</p><p><img src="https://gitee.com/ojbkxc/PicGo/raw/master/img/20200403190929.png" alt></p><p>然后就可以在写作中粘贴</p><p><img src="https://gitee.com/ojbkxc/PicGo/raw/master/img/20200403191609.png" alt></p><p><img src="https://gitee.com/ojbkxc/PicGo/raw/master/img/20200403191808.png" alt></p><p>也可以到相册里预览-复制图片链接上传过的文件链接，以及对上传图片的重命名和删除</p><p><img src="https://gitee.com/ojbkxc/PicGo/raw/master/img/20200403192157.png" alt></p><p>当然再讲一下剪贴板上传，我这里用QQ截图作为演示</p><p><img src="https://gitee.com/ojbkxc/PicGo/raw/master/img/20200403191519.png" alt></p><p>截完图之后就可以点击-剪贴板图片上传-上传</p><p><img src="https://gitee.com/ojbkxc/PicGo/raw/master/img/20200403192046.png" alt></p><p>到相册中进行查看</p><p><img src="https://gitee.com/ojbkxc/PicGo/raw/master/img/20200403191233.png" alt></p><p><img src="https://gitee.com/ojbkxc/PicGo/raw/master/img/20200403192247.png" alt></p><p><img src="https://gitee.com/ojbkxc/PicGo/raw/master/img/20200403192301.png" alt></p><p>暂时就写到这，吃饭去…</p><p>转载请注明：<a href="http://1232333.xyz/">い寻常づ的博客</a> » <a href="http://1232333.xyz/2020/04/03/搭建图床/">点击阅读原文</a></p>]]></content>
    
